{With eleven cards in the "round" suits WEST has a lot of playing strength. So when EAST bids 
a Limit Raise in \Hs WEST wants to know about Aces.

RKCBlackwood tells him that EAST has two Aces plus the trump Queen, so WEST can see that 6\H 
is practically a certainty.}

