[Student "S"]
{WEST decides it is unlikely that EAST is Aceless, so all he wants to know is the number of Aces EAST does have. 
He invokes RKC Blackwood.

Since no trump suit has been agreed, EAST bids as if \Ds, the 
last-bid suit prior to 4NT is agreed. EAST has two Key-cards plus the trump Queen, so she bids 5\S.

WEST bids 6\D. 
If EAST had just one Key-card, WEST would bid 5\D over the 5\C reply.}

